    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在税收问题上抨击工党，但难以削弱斯塔默</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sunak-hits-starmer-on-tax-but-loses-on-likability-in-uk-debate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 在英国首次与基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 进行竞选辩论时，使用了久经考验的保守党武器，反复警告工党领袖将提高税收。但他们在黄金时段的激烈电视辩论暴露了首相自己的弱点，也暴露了对手的弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sunak-hits-starmer-on-tax-but-loses-on-likability-in-uk-debate</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 00:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度大选意外：莫迪的失误以及接下来的走向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-election-2024-why-modi-bjp-s-lead-was-narrower-than-expected</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪在大选中遭遇重大挫折，他领导的印度人民党在议会下院失去了多数席位。莫迪表示，他将连任第三届，但人民党现在需要组建自十年前上台以来的首个联合政府。这种情况导致莫迪和人民党在政治上被一个复兴的反对派集团所削弱，该集团凭借竞选焦点成功夺取了地盘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/india-election-2024-why-modi-bjp-s-lead-was-narrower-than-expected</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 17:50:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾立法者为何采取行动限制总统权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/why-protesters-in-taiwan-are-angry-with-lawmakers-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾立法者于五月联手通过一项扩大其权力、使新总统赖清德执政更加困难的法案，导致台湾首都爆发了多年来最大规模的抗议活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/why-protesters-in-taiwan-are-angry-with-lawmakers-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
